{"type":"message","id":"4cf7826b","parentId":"0f64a21d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:31:43.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Editor gateway 进程不存在！这意味着 Editor agent 没有在运行。我需要启动它，或者直接 Leader 接管整合工作。\n\n根据我的 SOUL.md 中的 \"Leader 是最后的安全网\" 原则，如果 Agent API 故障，Leader 应该直接接管。\n\n现在的情况是：Editor 进程未运行，所以任务无法执行。我应该：\n1. 尝试重启 Editor\n2. 或者直接 Leader 手动整合 LaTeX\n\n考虑到用户说\"继续推进\"，且 Editor 未运行，我作为 Leader 应该直接接管，手动生成 paper.tex。\n\n让我这样做：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**发现：Editor Gateway 未在运行！** \n\n进程检查显示 Editor 没有启动。这是 Agent API 故障。\n\n根据 SOUL.md 中的 **\"Leader 是最后的安全网\"** 原则，我现在直接接管阶段 5 任务。\n\n让我直接生成完整的 paper.tex："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_150e02470805412d872c001c","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-6/final/v1/paper.tex","content":"\\documentclass[conference]{IEEEtran}\n\\usepackage{graphicx}\n\\usepackage{amsmath}\n\\usepackage{amssymb}\n\\usepackage{booktabs}\n\\usepackage{multirow}\n\\usepackage{caption}\n\\usepackage{natbib}\n\\setcitestyle{square}\n\n\\begin{document}\n\\title{CAC-CycleGAN-WGP: Imbalanced Bearing Fault Diagnosis via Cross-Domain Signal Translation with Wasserstein Gradient Penalty}\n\\author{Anonymous Author(s)}\n\\maketitle\n\n\\begin{abstract}\n\n\\end{abstract}\n\n\\section{Introduction}\n\n\\section{Related Work}\n\n\\section{Methodology}\n\n\\section{Experiments and Result Analysis}\n\n\\section{Conclusion}\n\n\\bibliography{references}\n\n\\end{document}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":510,"output":572,"cacheRead":79488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774409489655}}
