{"type":"message","id":"9cde53b2","parentId":"f9699a2c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:55:23.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"acs: 需要在 abstract_intro, experiments_p1, related_work 中替换。\n\n现在，我需要用 sed 批量替换 (be careful not to replace in citations like \\cite{35} that refer to other works). The rule: replace \"ACWGAN-GP\" with \"CAC-CycleGAN-WGP\" only when it's referring to our proposed method, not when it's citing other works like \"ACWGAN-GP [35]\".\n\nBut in our drafts, it's always used as our method, so safe to replace.\n\nLet's do:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_454e720b54d241cd8159f9c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -i 's/ACWGAN-GP/CAC-CycleGAN-WGP/g' /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-6/drafts/v3/abstract_intro.tex\nsed -i 's/ACWGAN-GP/CAC-CycleGAN-WGP/g' /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-6/drafts/v3/experiments_p1.tex\nsed -i 's/ACWGAN-GP/CAC-CycleGAN-WGP/g' /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-6/drafts/v3/related_work.tex\necho \"Method name replaced\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":1160,"output":423,"cacheRead":97152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774410918399}}
