ure the complex, non-linear distributions of vibration data in the high-frequency domain. In contrast, the CAC-CycleGAN-WGP provides a substantial boost in F1-score for the minority classes, indicating a reduction in the number of false negatives for rare fault types. For the most severe imbalance case (IR=1:50), our method maintains an accuracy of over 68.8\\%, whereas the baseline CNN drops significantly to 30.4\\%."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":503,"output":505,"cacheRead":124800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125808,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774411405100}}
