{"type":"message","id":"fe16d7ea","parentId":"9d03fa4d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T04:54:21.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来fig2和fig3在图环境中。让我看看fig1在哪里。也许它是“Figure 1”？让我搜索“figure 1”或“Fig. 1”。让我检查一下文件的早期部分，特别是引言部分。不过现在我需要开始修复这些问题了。\n\n我需要创建一个final/v3/目录，并彻底修正paper.tex。用户给了五个具体问题，我会逐一处理：\n\n1. **引用格式**：将natbib的square样式改为IEEEtran的标准数字引用，使用`\\bibliographystyle{IEEEtran}`，可能需要移除`\\usepackage{natbib}`，因为IEEEtran有自己的引用命令。\n\n2. **三张概念图双栏显示**：确保fig1, fig2, fig3使用`figure*`环境。\n\n3. **数据图拼贴**：对于每个数据图文件夹（如data_fig1等），需要将多个子图合并成一个图形，使用`subfigure`或`subcaption`。这是一个主要的图像处理任务。\n\n4. **排版对齐**：修复`\\begin{figure}`内联的问题，确保每个figure独立成行。\n\n5. **结论部分**：将conclusion的三个subsection合并为一段。\n\n让我先创建final/v3/目录，然后开始修复。首先复制v2的内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_57bcd0f2484f40298a6830cf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-6/final/v3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":143891,"output":698,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774414415424}}
